Male genitalia with one pair of parameres on urite IX. Parameres with 1 + 6 divisions, not quite attaining apex of penis. Penis and parameres attaining level of apex of urocoxites IX (
Fig. 9
). Length to width ratio of apical portion of penis about 2.0. Apical portion of penis 1.3 times length of basal portion.

